{{Infobox football club | clubname = ES Radès| image = Esrades.png| fullname = Étoile Sportive Radèsienne| nickname = | founded = 1948| ground = | capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 3|Ligue 3]]| season = [[2015–16 Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 3|2015–16]]| position = 3rd| }}
'''Étoile Sportive de Radès''' ({{lang-ar|'''النجم الرياضي الرادسي'''}}), often referred to as '''ESR''' is a basketball and football club from [[Radès]], [[Tunisia]]. Founded in 1948, the team plays in blue and white colors. They are competing in [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 3|Ligue 3]] as of [[2014–15 Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 3|2014–15]].
The team used to be called ''Union Sportive Radèsienne'' before 1965.
