'''Hot air balloon festivals''' are held annually in many places throughout the year, allowing [[hot air balloons]] operators to gather- as well as for the general public- to participate in various activities. They can include races; evening "[[night glow]]s", in which balloons are fired while remaining tethered to the ground; and rides.
